871
00:51:23.300 --> 00:51:24.920
Quero encontrar-me com ele.

872
00:51:25.760 --> 00:51:27.340
A sós.

873
00:51:28.680 --> 00:51:30.220
Podes tratar disso?

874
00:51:31.510 --> 00:51:33.810
