882
00:52:03.340 --> 00:52:04.340
Tens ciúmes.

883
00:52:04.510 --> 00:52:05.510
Eu?

884
00:52:05.670 --> 00:52:06.680
É fascinante.

885
00:52:06.840 --> 00:52:09.090
